You can easily change the height of a label.

image::labelHeight/labelHeight.png["Label Height",height=500]

Height
------
You might want to change the height of a label so that it fits a particular design... The default behaviour is for the text to be centered vertically in the frame of the label.

[source]
----
label.height = 200.0f;
----